General.Name: Egeli & Co. Agriculture Investment Trust Inc
General.Description: Egeli & Co. Agriculture Investment Trust Inc. specializes in direct and fund of fund investments. Within direct, it prefers to invest in growth capital investments in middle markets, buyouts, and turnaround companies. The fund prefers to invest in the agribusiness sector with a focus on food value chain focusing on companies based in Turkey. Within fund of fund, it prefers to invest in other private equity funds. It prefers to invest between TRY2 million ($0.68 million) and TRY10 million ($3.4 million) in companies with enterprise values between TRY20 million ($6.8 million) and TRY100 million ($34 million). It seeks to invest in undervalued companies based in Turkey.
